Text.string: You look tough. We're friends now.
Finally, someone who looks like they can take a bullet.
Hey. Wanna lift weights with me?
Heard you're a COV killer. Nice.
Glad you're here. Always safer with a Vault Hunter nearby.
It's so hot! How are you not melting?
Oh, Pandora... Just give us one day of rain.
In the cool of the night... that's when I fight.
It's as hot at night as during the day! HOW IS THAT POSSIBLE?
Let me at 'em. I'll wreck some faces.
Those COV assholes are going down. Sooner or later.
The Crimson Raiders need more warm bodies. I'm thinking we train skags and mount guns to their head. You into it?
I've got an itchy trigger finger. Think I should get that checked out?
If you ask me, the corporations made the bandits. This whole mess is on them.
Why are you talking to me? There are still bandits out there, yeah? Go kill some!
Pandora's a hellhole, but as long as the Crimson Raiders are around, there's... well, not hope... but a fighting chance.
You look pretty tough.
Nobody lives forever. But I'll be damned if I don't take some bandits with me.
Where do those psychos get those masks, anyway? Do they make 'em?
Humanity, huh? What a bunch of weirdos.
Get tough or get dead. That's how it goes on Pandora, anyway.
Some of us choose to live out on the edge. Feels more honest, somehow.
Sure, Pandora's at war. But when is it not?
I wasn't a fan of Atlas back in the day, but these new guns they're making lately are pretty slick. Maybe a corporation CAN do some good... But I doubt it.
We're with you, Vault Hunter. Wherever this ship takes us.
Lemme know if we're heading back to Pandora at some point. I got some scores to settle.
Glad to be on board, Vault Hunter. Thanks for havin' me.
With this ship, we can kill bandits all over the worlds!
We'll follow the COV wherever they go in this ship, and take the fight to them.
[yawn] I'm tired.
[yawn] Naptime.
[yawn] Gotta stretch the spine.
[yawns]
[yawn] I'm like a lion.
[yawn] I need more oxygen.
Later, Vault Hunter!
Go kick some ass!
Beat down some fanatics for me!
Take me with you next time!
If you die, I'll be pissed!
Good luck! Stay alive!
Remember, if something goes wrong, just keep shooting!
I told everyone you're a hero—don't make me a liar!
Peace out!
Later!
Ooh, I am SO gonna kill that guy...
Hahahaha!||—That didn't make me feel better.
I should get a hobby. Other that lifting.
Today's a new day.
Focus on the plan.
Mind over matter. That's what matters.
The system is rigged. Freaking corporations.
Something's gotta change. This can't be how things are supposed to be.
Ugh. I should be working out.
It's all so frickin' futile!
I ain't never gonna join a cult.
I'm freaking sick of this.
Um. Everyone is staring at me.
I'm just as good as that asshole. Why didn't they pick me?
My life is going just fine.
Just worked out and I'm swole!
Go team! I'm the team.
Ow-OW!
Punch 'em!
Face punchin' angels!
Yeah, boiii!
You got this, bruh!
Clap if you believe!
Everyone get the clap... going! Am I right?
[burp] Oh, that's gross.
[burp] I need a basket.
[burp] Oof, what was that?
Hey everyone, do the wave!
Hey, hi friend!
Anyone else right-handed?
Where my lefties at?
I salute you, buddy!
Hail to the king, baby!
